relevant_findings.general: Alert and in no apparent distress, laying in bed, looks comfortable
relevant_findings.ent: Ears and nose without visible erythema, masses, or trauma. Oropharynx without visible lesion, erythema or exudate. Moist mucus membranes.
relevant_findings.cv: Heart regular, no murmur, no S3, no S4. 2+ radial pulses bilaterally.
relevant_findings.resp: Lungs clear to auscultation with good air movement bilaterally. Breathing is non-labored on room air.
relevant_findings.gi: Abdomen soft, non-distended, tender in RUQ. Bowel sounds present. No rebound or guarding.
relevant_findings.gu: No suprapubic fullness or tenderness to palpation, no Foley.
relevant_findings.msk: Moves all extremities. No edema. Reproducible pain with palpation of chest.
relevant_findings.neuro: Alert, oriented, face symmetric, speech fluent.
